  - atc_3: Cocaine is pharmacologically related to local anesthetics and other otologicals and anesthetics, local and throat preparations.
  - atc_4: The chemical and functional group of  is local anesthetics and analgesics and anesthetics and esters of benzoic acid and anesthetics, local.
